---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "HVAC Services in Mississauga"
description: "Queensway Heating and Cooling offers furnace installation and repair, AC installation and repair, heat pumps, water heaters, and maintenance plans across Mississauga and the GTA."
---

<section class="page-hero page-hero--photo" aria-label="HVAC Services">
  <div class="page-hero__bg" aria-hidden="true">
    {% heroImage "/assets/img/hero/services-index.jpg", "Full range of HVAC services in the GTA", "100vw" %}
  </div>
  <div class="page-hero__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="page-hero__content">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>HVAC Services in Mississauga &amp; the GTA</h1>
      <p>From emergency furnace repair to new heat pump installations — Queensway Heating and Cooling has you covered.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="service-grid">
      {% for service in services %}
      <a href="/services/{{ service.slug }}/" class="service-card fade-in">
        <div class="service-card__title">{{ service.title }}</div>
        <p class="service-card__blurb">{{ service.blurb }}</p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% include "partials/cta-band.njk" %}
